Ranger Help for: rcompare
=========================

SYNTAX:      rcompare <item1> to <item2>
USAGE:       Any terrain.
SLOT COST:   0
BASE SP:     25

SUMMARY:
Compare two weapons or pieces of armor side by side, showing their
relative qualities. Higher ranked Rangers get more accurate and
detailed comparisons. Both items must be in your inventory.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: inspect, sharpen, treat
